description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Paros, Greece
-Hallstatt, Austria
-Amsterdam, Netherlands
-Sofia, Bulgaria
-Guanajuato, Mexico
-Cape Town, South Africa
-San Francisco, California, USA
-Marsaxlokk, Malta
-Tallinn, Estonia
-Mykonos, Greece
name: Beautiful Towns Around the World
